data.title: Famous birthdays list for February 17, 2024 includes celebrities Rene Russo, Joseph Gordon-Levitt
data.meta_description: Rene Russo and Joseph Gordon-Levitt share a birthday today. Check out our photo slideshow of celebrities and other famous people with birthdays on February 17, 2024 and find out a fun fact about each person.
data.text:
Birthday wishes go out to Rene Russo, Joseph Gordon-Levitt and all the other celebrities with birthdays today. Check out our slideshow below to see photos of famous people turning a year older on February 17th and learn an interesting fact about each of them.

Top celebrity birthdays on February 17, 2024

Actress Rene Russo turns 70

Fun fact: Went to the same high school as Ron Howard

Actor Lou Diamond Phillips turns 62

Fun fact: Appeared in an episode of ‘Quantum Leap’ last year

Comedian Larry the Cable Guy turns 61

Fun fact: His middle name is Lawrence

Director Michael Bay turns 60

Fun fact: His cousin Susan was married to Leonard Nimoy

Actress Denise Richards turns 53

Fun fact: Several of her early TV show appearances included episodes of ‘Doogie Howser’ and ‘Saved By the Bell’

Singer Billie Joe Armstrong turns 52

Fun fact: He and bandmates in Green Day were inducted into the Rock Hall by Fall Out Boy

Actor Jerry O’Connell turns 50

Fun fact: Has been the host of ‘Pictionary’ since 2022

Actor Jason Ritter turns 44

Fun fact: Reportedly appeared as one of the zombie clickers in an episode of ‘The Last of Us’

Pop icon Paris Hilton turns 44

Fun fact: Celebrated her 21st birthday with multiple parties across the globe

Actor Joseph Gordon-Levitt turns 43

Fun fact: Has one Daytime Emmy nomination

Singer Ed Sheeran turns 33

Fun fact: Has two children, Jupiter and Lyra

More celebrities with birthdays today

Actor Christina Pickles (“The Wedding Singer,” ″St. Elsewhere”) is 89. Actor Brenda Fricker (“My Left Foot,” “So I Married an Axe Murderer”) is 79. Actor Becky Ann Baker (“Girls,” ″Freaks and Geeks”) is 71. Actor Richard Karn (“Home Improvement”) is 68. Singer Chante Moore is 57. Guitarist Tim Mahoney of 311 is 54. Actor Dominic Purcell (“Prison Break”) is 54. Country singer Bryan White is 50. Actor Kelly Carlson (“Nip/Tuck”) is 48. Actor Conrad Ricamora (“How to Get Away With Murder”) is 45. TV co-host Daphne Oz (“The Chew”) is 38. Actor Chord Overstreet (“Glee”) is 35. Actor Meaghan Martin (“10 Things I Hate About You,” “Camp Rock”) is 32. Actor Sasha Pieterse (“Pretty Little Liars”) is 28.

Other popular or historical birthdays on February 17th

William Cadbury, English chocolate maker

Thomas Watson, founder of IBM

Hal Holbrook, actor
